target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4qeAnOX-UCk</a>"},{"pid":"83152f316467340648b9c7c15a367fb821789002","tid":308842,"uid":124891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T18:17:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>做乜變左罵戰post，鍾意聽 pop punk都唔算差啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  大家 under 同一 genre</blockquote><br />\n你要問下隻狗做咩係到吠啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\npop punk 同 punk rock 絕對唔係under 同一個genre<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\npop punk係受現代流行曲影響所發展既分支<br />\n由 green day, the offspring,bad religion等等既 band所帶起<br />\n<br />\n準確d講 pop punk係由punk rock 加入流行曲元素發展而成,所以pop punk係under punk rock既一種genre</blockquote><br />\nbad religion都算？</blockquote><br />\n佢地既定位其實係係pop 同 rock之間<br />\n佢地係之後發展pop punk既雛形<br />\n歌詞由評擊政府轉變成諷刺時弊甚至愛情都有<br />\n部分曲風偏向使用簡單拍子同單一重覆既melody 呢d都係流行曲元素<br />\n樂器方面比較diversed 唔似傳統 punk rock咁狂掃power chord同downward strumming 而且有唔少guitar solo既出現<br />\n可以聽下呢首 其實唔難聽出同傳統punk rock既分別<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/B7nyJLynJiI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FB7nyJLynJiI&d=T%2BvWPpznbk5CqmqUx5SEAI9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=2ca02ff9\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/B7nyJLynJiI</a>"},{"pid":"9feb7667812acd4789dd0c6f62d2e12ee8e3cf5b","tid":308842,"uid":124891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T18:21:51.000Z","msg":"其實嘈嚟冇咩意思 一隊band冇絕對既定位<br />\n冇絕對既genre <br />\n就好似 imagine dragon都係介於 indie, alternative rock之間 最近玩埋電音<br />\n冇人可以幫一隊band絕對咁分辨genre<br />\n可能連隊band自己都答唔到你<br />\n音樂都係用嚟聽㗎姐 合則來不合則去<br />\n冇必要分得咁細 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89a743f4565589fa5160d7feea6b28d197d8be7b","tid":308842,"uid":89282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T03:24:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主咁對隻痴狗認真啦<br />\n成熟啲啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/c